txt.en: Grodris, the matron of the Wintersebb drakes, returns to the Isendeep Mine to defend her brood. Gather forces and destroy her.
Do not succumb to defeat while fighting Grodris
Grodris returns to defend her brood in the Isendeep. Defeat her and gain power for your side of the battle in the Ettenmoors.
Defeat Grodris, the matron of the Wintersebb
Defeat Grodris, the matron of the Wintersebb
Grodris, the matron of the Wintersebb, now stalks the Isendeep mine in the Ettenmoors.\n\nDestroy her and earn power for your side of the battle.
Grodris, the matron of the Wintersebb, now stalks the mountains of the Ettenmoors. If left unchecked, there is no telling what this unbound beast will do to Orc and Elf alike.\n\nDestroy her.
